# Day 1 - Product Metrics

## Swiggy
Retention: % of users who order again
Churn: users who stop ordering

## Amazon
Conversion: % of users who make a purchase
DAU/MAU: active users on platform

## Case 1: Churn increase (Swiggy)
- Poor food quality
- Delivery delays
- High prices

## Case 2: Conversion drop (Amazon)
- Pricing issues
- Checkout friction
- Poor product descriptions
